| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2676 — Recovery Inhibition (nokoyawa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d4df813f-964a-5c3f-9a0e-98ea780e1518"
